"Starchaser is equipped with an alien-tech propulsion system that, along with "
"its sleek, aerodynamic design, bestows it with both speed and "
"manoeuvrability. The hull itself is made out of dense layers of alien "
"materials, providing an unprecedented level of durability. Finally, despite "
"the fact that the compact design leaves us with only limited options for "
"modular weapon and support systems, we've managed to improve firepower over "
"the Dragon design.\n"
"\n"
